<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan>, Hansen und
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> der Keppfen,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, und <add>wegen</add>
<expan>ir<ex>r</ex></expan> schafe, die sie vor uns zu den heiligen behabt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz dy ir sein, also daz kein auszman
                        daran weder teil noch gemein habe, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief und
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> darauff wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, und senden darümb czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Hansen Höhel,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit euch davon zu reden, und
                        biten wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiss<ex>iklich</ex></expan>, waz der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener in <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sache etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Mathei
                            <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
